dct_description_sm: Map of Sydney region, Broken Bay - Ebenezer - Minto, showing four classes of roads, railroads, distances, some facilities. Index to localities. "B.C.V. 105610. R. 176407." "Copyright Regd. N.R.M.A. All right reserved." Includes 2 freeway interchange diagrams: Southern approach -- Northern approach [Sydney Harbour Bridge] on verso. Index to streets and tourist sites on verso.
dct_creator_sm: National Roads and Motorists' Association. Touring Department. Cartographic Section
